articles.author: Martin Goillandeau, Hilary Clarke
articles.title: Jacques Delors, statesman who shaped European Union, dies at 98 - CNN
articles.description: Former European Commission President Jacques Delors, a key figure in the creation of the euro currency, has died aged 98 on Wednesday, according to a statement from the Jacques Delors Institute, a think tank he founded.
